ZH: 我已经有一个月没有吃肉了，我正在尝试素食。
EN: I haven't eaten meat for a month now, I am trying out vegetarianism.

ZH: 我的朋友选择了素食，对健康有好处。
EN: My friend has chosen to go vegetarian, it's good for health.

ZH: 素食可以减少对动物的伤害。
EN: Vegetarianism can reduce harm to animals.

ZH: 我愿意尝试一下素食主义生活。
EN: I am willing to give vegetarianism a try.

ZH: 素食可以帮助保护环境。
EN: Vegetarianism can help protect the environment.

ZH: 我每周至少有三天选择素食。
EN: I choose vegetarian options at least three days a week.

ZH: 素食对身体好处多多。
EN: Vegetarianism has many benefits for the body.

ZH: 我喜欢尝试各种素食食谱。
EN: I enjoy trying out different vegetarian recipes.

ZH: 我的素食主义生活改变了我的生活方式。
EN: My vegetarianism has changed my way of living.

ZH: 素食可以帮助减肥。
EN: Vegetarianism can help with weight loss.

ZH: 我发现素食可以让我更健康。
EN: I find that vegetarianism makes me healthier.

ZH: 素食也可以很好吃。
EN: Vegetarian food can be delicious too.

ZH: 我每餐都会选择至少一道素食菜。
EN: I make sure to have at least one vegetarian dish in every meal.

ZH: 素食可以预防一些慢性疾病。
EN: Vegetarianism can prevent certain chronic diseases.

ZH: 我经常购买素食杂志学习新的菜谱。
EN: I often buy vegetarian magazines to learn new recipes.

ZH: 素食主义者需要注意摄入足够的营养。
EN: Vegetarians need to make sure they get enough nutrients.

ZH: 我们这个团队每周一次举办素食晚宴。
EN: Our team hosts a vegetarian dinner once a week.

ZH: 素食可以让人更有活力。
EN: Vegetarianism can give people more energy.

ZH: 我的素食餐都很丰富。
EN: My vegetarian meals are always rich in variety.

ZH: 素食是一种健康的生活方式。
